text: i signed up for an ielts online course
at lango and it turns out to be the best
decision that i had ever made
[Music]
hello guys my name is quinoa i am now 18
years old and i am studying
international business and national
economics university
i had my ielts test in last december and
thanks to lego i achieved the score of
7.5 i signed up for an ielts online
course at lago and it turns out to be
the best decision that i had ever made
you know learning ielts is very
challenging you have to remember all the
vocabularies and grammar structures and
the way to use them correctly as well
but my teachers at lango once taught me
that i have to keep practicing and
learning again and again until again i
create a logical writing structure and i
can be more consistent with my ideas but
don't lose heart okay
i believe that your ir certificate will
help you open the door to many
opportunities such as education
employment promotion or even immigration
since it is widely accepted and trusted
across the world
i got the idea of visualizing my future
with an ielts certificate from a special
method called nlp
when i was taking a course at lango nlp
actually helps me a lot it changed my
whole mindset and also helped me to
develop myself discipline
although it was an online class but i
was really surprised by its
effectiveness because every class is
only consists of six students i had
plenty of time to interact with my
teachers and improve my score i also
feel grateful for having such wonderful
teachers who always provided me with the
most effective method by taking up their
daily challenges i finally got into the
habits of learning english every day and
after six months of working so hard to
improve every aspect of my english
language ability i finally got 7.5
overall which is 8.5 in listening and
8.0 in reading now i can read english
newspaper i also can use complex
sentences to express my opinions which
of course helped me a lot in
communicating with native speakers
and also writing is not a huge problem
anymore because i now have a larger
range of vocabularies and grammar
structures that i know i can use
if you want to conquer the ielts
remember this nothing is impossible if
you have enough motivation to keep
following your dreams
if i can do it with mango so can you
